title: China's CATL says will supply battery cells to Bosch - Nasdaq.com
text: BEIJING, Sept 5 (Reuters) - China's top battery maker Contemporary Amperex Technology Co Ltd (CATL)  said on Thursday it will supply battery cells to German auto supplier Bosch [RIC:RIC:ROBG.UL].
CATL will supply battery cells for Bosch's 48-volt battery system globally, company said in a statement.
